ObsoleteData.Message: enableInteriorCollisions property is deprecated and is no longer required and has no effect on the particle system.
rate property is deprecated. Use rateOverTime or rateOverDistance instead.
rateMultiplier property is deprecated. Use rateOverTimeMultiplier or rateOverDistanceMultiplier instead.
ParticleSystemEmissionType no longer does anything. Time and Distance based emission are now both always active.
meshScale property is deprecated.Please use scale instead.
randomDirection property is deprecated. Use randomDirectionAmount instead.
birth0 property is deprecated. Use AddSubEmitter, RemoveSubEmitter, SetSubEmitterSystem and GetSubEmitterSystem instead.
birth1 property is deprecated. Use AddSubEmitter, RemoveSubEmitter, SetSubEmitterSystem and GetSubEmitterSystem instead.
collision0 property is deprecated. Use AddSubEmitter, RemoveSubEmitter, SetSubEmitterSystem and GetSubEmitterSystem instead.
collision1 property is deprecated. Use AddSubEmitter, RemoveSubEmitter, SetSubEmitterSystem and GetSubEmitterSystem instead.
death0 property is deprecated. Use AddSubEmitter, RemoveSubEmitter, SetSubEmitterSystem and GetSubEmitterSystem instead.
death1 property is deprecated. Use AddSubEmitter, RemoveSubEmitter, SetSubEmitterSystem and GetSubEmitterSystem instead.
flipU property is deprecated. Use ParticleSystemRenderer.flip.x instead.
flipV property is deprecated. Use ParticleSystemRenderer.flip.y instead.
useRandomRow property is deprecated. Use rowMode instead.
